<plot>There's a man sitting at a table, his face and hand dirty from ash. While he is playing with fire, people are screaming; agonizing cries, like creatures facing death. The table is covered with matchboxes. This is not a human screaming, it is a matchstick! One by one boxes full of matchsticks face a horrible death as the arsonist sets them on fire. But one matchstick box is moving and its escape is imminent.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?540771</url></doc>
